  "original_title": "\u0da9\u0dbd\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dcf\u0dba\u0db8\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0dba\u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dba \u0db1\u0dd1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "No budget support from the Dallas team",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The 13 members of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peremane, who left the government and went to the opposition, decided to refrain from voting in the interim budget vote, says Mr. G. L. Peiris, Member of Parliament.",
        "He mentioned this while attending the opening of the main office of the Free National Assembly, which was established by the 13 people who left the government and joined the opposition.",
        "Mr. G. L. Peiris also said that he took that action to express his objection to not giving any space to his group to comment in the interim budget debate."
      ],
